  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/5230ebb4b53ba70d0bf622ef089f2856.avif?t=1722585763\" width=480 height=80 /></span><br>Five Gods of Kung Fu is a story driven Beat 'em Up with a totally unique control scheme. <br><br>Explore the Far East to discover, train and master various Kung Fu Styles – each with distinct mechanics.<br><br>The unique input scheme requires dedication and skill and gives you the feeling of truly mastering a fighting technique. It’s the next best thing to actually learning Kung Fu.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/17b70c326bb7060e96b98d0801b127cb.avif?t=1722585763\" width=480 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DRUNKEN</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/6ec7310ca5b2318a45a3eee0505104c6.apng?t=1722585763\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/6ec7310ca5b2318a45a3eee0505104c6.poster.avif?t=1722585763\" class=\"bb_img\" width=160 height=160 /></picture></span><br>Drunken Kung Fu uses <strong>dodging </strong>to gain momentum. Use that imbalance to your advantage and strike your enemy with even more force.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SNAKE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/e0f0987f6ec0535c8269d82c19853271.poster.avif?t=1722585763\" width=160 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/e0f0987f6ec0535c8269d82c19853271.webm?t=1722585763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Snake Style focuses on targeting weak spots of your enemy. <strong>Time your inputs</strong> perfectly to break through your opponents defenses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TIGER</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/5f35debf4644014f3180c2b240de34a8.poster.avif?t=1722585763\" width=160 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/5f35debf4644014f3180c2b240de34a8.webm?t=1722585763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>With the Tiger Style, you can <strong>parry </strong>your opponents attacks to create an opening for powerful <strong>charged attacks</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MANTIS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/731370fcc0579a0fa1ad5441a51d262c.poster.avif?t=1722585763\" width=160 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/731370fcc0579a0fa1ad5441a51d262c.webm?t=1722585763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The Mantis Style lets you <strong>trap</strong> your enemies attacks and retaliate when they are stuck.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/3c43f5b95649f157d7bcdc53553dc6e7.avif?t=1722585763\" width=480 height=80 /></span><br><br>In order to master, you first need to practice!<br><br>Five Gods of Kung Fu features a unique input method using the face buttons of the controller to input motion like movements. <br><br>This motion like input may need some getting used to, but becomes very intuitive after a while. You will truly feel like you are mastering a new technique.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/c933321b6f9494b0389c26caa74a5774.poster.avif?t=1722585763\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/c933321b6f9494b0389c26caa74a5774.webm?t=1722585763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/c933321b6f9494b0389c26caa74a5774.mp4?t=1722585763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/58f77c408d717ca63f25ea8c528f97c1.avif?t=1722585763\" width=480 height=80 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic Kung Fu action!<br></li><li>Explore a large, interconnected 2D world<br></li><li>Discover, practice and master famous fighting styles<br></li><li>Bad-ass boss battles!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/5230ebb4b53ba70d0bf622ef089f2856.avif?t=1722585763\" width=480 height=80 /></span><br>Five Gods of Kung Fu is a story driven Beat 'em Up with a totally unique control scheme. <br><br>Explore the Far East to discover, train and master various Kung Fu Styles – each with distinct mechanics.<br><br>The unique input scheme requires dedication and skill and gives you the feeling of truly mastering a fighting technique. It’s the next best thing to actually learning Kung Fu.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/17b70c326bb7060e96b98d0801b127cb.avif?t=1722585763\" width=480 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DRUNKEN</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/6ec7310ca5b2318a45a3eee0505104c6.apng?t=1722585763\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/6ec7310ca5b2318a45a3eee0505104c6.poster.avif?t=1722585763\" class=\"bb_img\" width=160 height=160 /></picture></span><br>Drunken Kung Fu uses <strong>dodging </strong>to gain momentum. Use that imbalance to your advantage and strike your enemy with even more force.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SNAKE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/e0f0987f6ec0535c8269d82c19853271.poster.avif?t=1722585763\" width=160 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/e0f0987f6ec0535c8269d82c19853271.webm?t=1722585763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Snake Style focuses on targeting weak spots of your enemy. <strong>Time your inputs</strong> perfectly to break through your opponents defenses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TIGER</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/5f35debf4644014f3180c2b240de34a8.poster.avif?t=1722585763\" width=160 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/5f35debf4644014f3180c2b240de34a8.webm?t=1722585763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>With the Tiger Style, you can <strong>parry </strong>your opponents attacks to create an opening for powerful <strong>charged attacks</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MANTIS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/731370fcc0579a0fa1ad5441a51d262c.poster.avif?t=1722585763\" width=160 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/731370fcc0579a0fa1ad5441a51d262c.webm?t=1722585763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The Mantis Style lets you <strong>trap</strong> your enemies attacks and retaliate when they are stuck.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/3c43f5b95649f157d7bcdc53553dc6e7.avif?t=1722585763\" width=480 height=80 /></span><br><br>In order to master, you first need to practice!<br><br>Five Gods of Kung Fu features a unique input method using the face buttons of the controller to input motion like movements. <br><br>This motion like input may need some getting used to, but becomes very intuitive after a while. You will truly feel like you are mastering a new technique.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/c933321b6f9494b0389c26caa74a5774.poster.avif?t=1722585763\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/c933321b6f9494b0389c26caa74a5774.webm?t=1722585763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/c933321b6f9494b0389c26caa74a5774.mp4?t=1722585763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2755020/extras/58f77c408d717ca63f25ea8c528f97c1.avif?t=1722585763\" width=480 height=80 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic Kung Fu action!<br></li><li>Explore a large, interconnected 2D world<br></li><li>Discover, practice and master famous fighting styles<br></li><li>Bad-ass boss battles!</li></ul>",
